{"tid":473601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母啦 竟然話大快活請人做打手","createTime":"2017-11-19T11:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T11:52:11.000Z","uid":25899,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79e9b24fd3ca094f6236f8bd18ed7b5e78139023","tid":473601,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"大快活請左幾多人做打手？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/473177/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/473177/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n老老實實睇到把撚火<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/190704_e829f80a90dba84917e9e884b0939dd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F190704_e829f80a90dba84917e9e884b0939dd6.png&h=8e4c4141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/190712_148baeaa656d7a990f5c5224ec561687.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F190712_148baeaa656d7a990f5c5224ec561687.png&h=bb8bcad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/190722_fd1d572ac0a93259f22d406f347b7ebf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F190722_fd1d572ac0a93259f22d406f347b7ebf.png&h=d52511a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/190724_01bf06625767330550bdf2ad918eb678.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F190724_01bf06625767330550bdf2ad918eb678.png&h=dac416cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/190726_05819cd6aa9b426546a9a3987d215eb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F190726_05819cd6aa9b426546a9a3987d215eb6.png&h=9d6df9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己一個禮拜七日早餐午餐都係出邊食 咁以前朝早就日撚日食大家樂嘅 仲特登申請埋club會員 每張單儲1分 3分當5蚊 5分當10蚊<br />\n<br />\n直到有一排真係頂唔撚順<br />\nD吉豬有陣洋蔥味 再加上乾撚到可以𠝹損你個口<br />\n而且為左掩飾偷工減料 勁撚多炸粉 3~4成都係脂肪 難撚食到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話大家樂早餐好食個D 我真係屌你老味呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/191500_17fc74ac68c5482fe4e720c2d98c2f75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F191500_17fc74ac68c5482fe4e720c2d98c2f75.jpg&h=3ee568f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩屌 一睇幅圖 咁撚大塊 係咪好撚正呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家樂the fucking best choice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/191613_0fff6f15f865f1d8bb3dd88bf22dd729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F191613_0fff6f15f865f1d8bb3dd88bf22dd729.jpg&h=09c2762e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食屎啦屌你老味臭閪 圖上面剩低既全部都係炸粉 / 肥肉<br />\n已經唔係第一次係咁 愈黎愈變本加厲 牛乳滑蛋仲可以勁撚多鹽咸撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192125_ea507573ba1b7bfea6bbd715e4aa4c10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192125_ea507573ba1b7bfea6bbd715e4aa4c10.jpg&h=c80b2bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦 到魚柳係咪睇落正正常常咁呀？<br />\n初初我都係咁覺得 食落其實都叫收貨<br />\n但自從轉撚左食大快活之後 先知乜野叫比較<br />\n大家樂塊魚柳一定擺得勁耐 又乾身 又勁嚡<br />\n細唔細塊我唔知 但我食開大快活塊魚柳就一定大撚過大家樂嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得我係打手 咪下我八達通record <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機八達通係得咁多 冇得再show遠d<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/193149_c6a167dedeee02c2e01c6a82e6b80cc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F193149_c6a167dedeee02c2e01c6a82e6b80cc7.jpg&h=e9f47915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/193150_c27d98c35fd7004b33fc090512da6ed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F193150_c27d98c35fd7004b33fc090512da6ed9.jpg&h=13c36528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時隨手影send返比屋企人/朋友講自己食緊咩個陣影嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192542_80ecf3ea6f10a7c4ab4e0817366c7a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192542_80ecf3ea6f10a7c4ab4e0817366c7a0a.jpg&h=a7a1b612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192614_a61fdca2fb7e14e90bb7427bd6305ad3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192614_a61fdca2fb7e14e90bb7427bd6305ad3.jpg&h=de3aa90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192614_050120bec76572fd14b7d2a3d3e8fc1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192614_050120bec76572fd14b7d2a3d3e8fc1b.jpg&h=7c131450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192615_d47779af8b84d8bac86e28c9549ba360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192615_d47779af8b84d8bac86e28c9549ba360.jpg&h=4f61cdbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192616_0ad083809e95728b206e9c8a3f4602f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192616_0ad083809e95728b206e9c8a3f4602f6.jpg&h=5dea2f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192617_a5f0432d9f95a0e8dbd5690256e56b1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192617_a5f0432d9f95a0e8dbd5690256e56b1b.jpg&h=d9058297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192618_811bcc1a63850ca8e4fc8eb566798bec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192618_811bcc1a63850ca8e4fc8eb566798bec.jpg&h=f69d943a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/192619_df96b85c647f054b910239d4e8e17acc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F192619_df96b85c647f054b910239d4e8e17acc.jpg&h=b694fe5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉食大快活之後 份人都開朗左呀屌你老味 日日朝早唔洗再燥</span></span><br />\n呀屌 出呢個post勾起我大家樂嘅不快回憶 諗起又燥 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6a9e54895953d218d24b1a8459e3710ce336c64","tid":473601,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"ching sick ball<br />\nbtw 點解唔開係飲食台"},{"pid":"f1669559b06a0cdcad15c8e8ad0a1e38bc699d46","tid":473601,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"網上既野<br />\n何必太認真<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3508f1f00d5ea810d73b5d15315aea1eaa6cc519","tid":473601,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching sick ball<br />\nbtw 點解唔開係飲食台</blockquote><br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25720a787b303af4059f8e5d3fb18a5af84a823a","tid":473601,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets